OL,3,CEducation minister in crackdown on
OL,4,Cmobile phones in schools
OL,6,FSchools in Northern Ireland have been
OL,7,Fadvised to restrict the use of mobile
OL,8,Fphones across the day.
OL,10,FStormont Education Minister Paul Givan
OL,11,Fissued new guidance to schools over
OL,12,Frestricting the personal use of mobile
OL,13,Fphones throughout the school day,
OL,14,Fincluding at break and lunchtimes.
OL,16,FWhile many schools in the region
OL,17,Falready restrict mobile phone usage,
OL,18,Fthe guidance is aimed to ensure a more
OL,19,Fconsistent approach across all schools.
