OL,3,CEducation minister in crackdown on
OL,4,Cmobile phones in schools
OL,6,FThere is also a pilot programme of
OL,7,Fphone free solutions, aimed at
OL,8,Fpreventing pupils from using their
OL,9,Fphones during the school day.
OL,11,FThese involve a pocket-sized fabric
OL,12,Fpouch with a magnetic latch that is
OL,13,Fsealed at the beginning of the school
OL,14,Fday and opened using a special
OL,15,Funlocking base.
OL,17,FMr Givan said the guidance is aimed at
OL,18,Fsupporting teachers in their work.
