OL,3,CEducation minister in crackdown on
OL,4,Cmobile phones in schools
OL,6,F"Growing evidence shows that phones
OL,7,Fdistract children from learning and
OL,8,Fthat limiting access to mobile phones
OL,9,Fduring the school day can have a
OL,10,Fpositive impact on academic engagement
OL,11,Fand achievement," he said.
OL,13,F"Many countries across the world are
OL,14,Fincreasingly taking steps to stop
OL,15,Fphone use at school.
OL,17,F"The new guidance will ensure schools
OL,18,Fin Northern Ireland are fully aware of
OL,19,Fthe latest evidence and have practical
OL,20,Fadvice around different approaches to
OL,21,Frestricting phone use.
