OL,3,CEducation minister in crackdown on
OL,4,Cmobile phones in schools
OL,6,F"Changes around phone use in schools
OL,7,Fcan make the world of difference in
OL,8,Four classrooms.
OL,10,F"Restricting their use during the
OL,11,Fschool day allows children to better
OL,12,Fconcentrate, engage and learn, as well
OL,13,Fas enjoying 'phone-free' break and
OL,14,Flunchtimes so they can play, have fun,
OL,15,Fparticipate in sports and socialise
OL,16,Fwith their friends."
OL,18,F"Today's guidance will support our
OL,19,Fteachers to allow them to do what they
OL,20,Fdo best ` teach."
